{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase annual Pension Protection Fund compensation for pre-1997 service",
        "additional_details": "Rampant cost of living aside, we feel it is not fair that pension contribution rights, locked within the PPF and accrued before 1997 are not annually increased.\r\n\r\nWe think PPF Pre 1997 accrued pension contribution rights should be treated equally to any other pensionable rights. \r\n",
        "background": "We want the Government to include annual increases (indexation) in Pension Protection Fund compensation for pre-1997 service.",
